subject: Archive the plan
description:
After all other tasks complete:
1. Create folder `fix-track-plan-sessions` in `./plans/completed`
2. Rename the plan to a name befitting the actual plan contents
3. Move it into `./plans/completed/fix-track-plan-sessions`
4. Read the session IDs from `./plans/completed/fix-track-plan-sessions`
5. For each session ID, move `~/.claude/tasks/<session-id>` directory to `./plans/completed/fix-track-plan-sessions/tasks`
